EXTRACTED VALUE: Burnout Revenge is the best arcade racer to date. Welcome to next-gen.
The kind of logical thinking it requires of you in the forensic mode is unheard of in action games.
Even with a new developer, the game doesn't miss a beat.
A fantastic effort, and worth the cash to own this one outright.
Overall the gameplay of Burnout Paradise is spot on and great fun.
As a co-op experience and as a tactical shooter, Rainbow Six Vegas sets a new benchmark for the gaming industry.
